Create Yocto build tree toolchain Docker Profile
execute the test only when the build_tree_path parameter are set. Set build_tree_path  to blank to skip this test case.
a) In "Preferences" Window -> click "New".
b) In "Create new profile" Window -> insert an identical profile name -> click "Ok".
c) In "Preferences" Window -> check "Build and launch using container" -> Select "Build directory" -> click "Edit"
d) In prompt window, select Mount a host directory -> click "Browse..." -> locate to SDK path setup  -> copy the Directory -> paste to "Container path" -> click "Ok" -> click "Apply" -> click "Apply and Close".
